<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Happy Birthday Nita! 🎉</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe0f0, #ffd1d1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
      color: #d81b60;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      animation: pop 1s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #ff4081;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(216,27,96,0.08);
    }
    .video-container {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(216,27,96,0.07);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    @keyframes pop {
      0% { transform: scale(1);}
      100% { transform: scale(1.12);}
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #ad1457;
      opacity: 0.65;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>🥳 Happy Birthday Nita! 🎂❤️</h1>
  <div class="video-container">
    <iframe width="340" height="191"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MmdBrYiftzI?autoplay=1&amp;start=0"
      title="Birthday Song"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>
  </div>
  <p>
    Wishing you a day full of laughter, love, and sweet surprises! 💖✨<br>
    May all your dreams come true this year. 🌟<br>
    You deserve all the happiness in the world, not just today, but every single moment you’re around.<br>
    I hope your day is as amazing as you are! 🥰✨<br>
    Enjoy every moment and keep smiling! 😄🎁<br>
    <span style="font-size:22px;">From someone who really cares about you and can’t stop thinking about you 😉❤️</span>
  </p>
  <div class="footer">
    &mdash; Made with ❤️ <span style="font-size:18px;">by KSV555</span>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
